% ROUTINES
%
% Files
%   A_to_f          - Calculates A(f), in the frequency domain.
%   arfitcaps       - Capsule to call the arfit.m routine for VAR estimation
%   asymp_pdc       - Core routine to compute connectivity measure.
%   cmlsm           - VAR least squares estimator
%   coh_alg         - Compute coherence function from SS
%   gct_alg         - Perform GCT and IGCT
%   mcarns          - VAR Nuttall-Strand algorithm
%   mcarvm          - VAR estimation using Vieira Morf algorithm
%   mvar            - Capsule for VAR estimation
%   mvarresidue     - Residues test for whiteness
%   pdc_alg         - Compute partial directed coherence measure and asymptotic statistics.
%   pdc_xplot       - Connectivity plot in matrix layout with power spectra in the main diagonal 
%   ss_alg          - Calculates the Spectral density (SS)
%   standardize     - Standardization preprocessing of time series